sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>/models
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8001/TCP (or 7071/TCP)

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Loading

    MM->>Puller: loadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8084/TCP
    Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
    Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller->>FS: Write model files to /models/{modelId}
    Puller->>Adapter: loadModel(modelId, localPath)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8085/TCP
    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model<br/>(gRPC 8001 or HTTP 8001 or gRPC 7071)<br/>plaintext, no auth
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Load confirmation
    Adapter-->>Puller: LoadModelResponse
    Puller-->>MM: LoadModelResponse

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Unloading

    MM->>Puller: unloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8084/TCP
    Puller->>Adapter: unloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8085/TCP
    Adapter->>Runtime: Unload model<br/>plaintext
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Unload confirmation
    Adapter-->>Puller: UnloadModelResponse
    Puller->>FS: Delete model files
    Puller-->>MM: UnloadModelResponse

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 3: Runtime Status / Model Size

    MM->>Puller: runtimeStatus() / predictModelSize()<br/>gRPC plaintext 8084/TCP
    Puller->>Adapter: runtimeStatus() / predictModelSize()<br/>gRPC plaintext 8085/TCP
    Adapter-->>Puller: Status/Size response
    Puller-->>MM: Status/Size response
